<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to Chat App</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f4f7f6; padding: 40px 0;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #28a745; padding: 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">Welcome to Chat App!</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px;">
                            <h2 style="color: #333333; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 22px;">Hi <%= userName %>,</h2>
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                We are absolutely thrilled to have you on board! Chat App is designed to bring you closer to your friends, family, and colleagues with seamless messaging.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                Dive right in, set up your profile, and start your first conversation. If you need any help getting started, our support team is always here for you.
                            </p>
                            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                <a href="#" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #28a745; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Get Started</a>
                            </div>
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 0;">
                                Happy chatting,<br>
                                <strong>The Chat App Team</strong>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;">
                            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999; margin: 0;">
                                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Chat App. All rights reserved.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
